{"ID":"20260305082130-3tloe19","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3tloe19","title":"函数指针","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-0wqnyxc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-0wqnyxc"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 函数指针\ndate created: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 11:45:46 晚上\ndate modified: 星期四, 十月 23日 2025, 12:00:39 凌晨\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1adi7f3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1adi7f3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数指针是一种特殊的指针，它存储的不是变量的地址，而是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"函数的内存地址"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。通过函数指针，我们可以像操作变量一样操作函数，例如将函数作为参数传递给其他函数，或者将函数存储在数据结构中。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l2ftc4o","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l2ftc4o","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 函数指针的声明"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-epqimx8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-epqimx8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数指针的声明语法与普通指针类似，但需要指明它所指向的函数的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"返回类型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"参数列表"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-x5pcthq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-x5pcthq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ReturnType (*pointer_name)(ParameterType1, ParameterType2, …);"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-oeir43t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oeir43t","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"关键点："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"(*pointer_name)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 必须用括号括起来，以表明 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"pointer_name"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一个指针，而不是一个返回指针的函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-n88tv0s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-n88tv0s","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ikmv8dg","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ikmv8dg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 假设有以下函数\nint add(int a, int b) {\n    return a + b;\n}\n\nvoid greet(const char* name) {\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Hello, \" \u003c\u003c name \u003c\u003c \"!\" \u003c\u003c std::endl;\n}\n\n// 声明一个函数指针，指向返回 int，接受两个 int 参数的函数\nint (*add_ptr)(int, int);\n// 声明一个函数指针，指向返回 void，接受一个 const char* 参数的函数\nvoid (*greet_ptr)(const char*);\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gixpzv6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gixpzv6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 函数指针的初始化与赋值"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-u27v0hj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u27v0hj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将函数的地址赋给函数指针。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"\u0026amp;"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 运算符是可选的，因为函数名本身在表达式中就会被隐式转换为其地址。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ta43zgo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ta43zgo","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-pjn41ux","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pjn41ux","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 初始化\nint (*add_ptr)(int, int) = \u0026add; // 显式取地址\n// 或者\nint (*add_ptr_alt)(int, int) = add; // 隐式转换为地址\n\n// 赋值\ngreet_ptr = \u0026greet; // 显式取地址\n// 或者\ngreet_ptr = greet; // 隐式转换为地址\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-skxe545","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-skxe545","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. 通过函数指针调用函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-n2hxlgy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-n2hxlgy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通过函数指针调用函数有两种方式：显式解引用和隐式解引用。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2l3cr3n","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2l3cr3n","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-t95tx0s","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-t95tx0s","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-lg7u073","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-lg7u073","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"显式解引用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠(*pointer_name)(arguments);"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ml5eop7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ml5eop7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-rxvqztf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-rxvqztf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"隐式解引用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠pointer_name(arguments);"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 更常用，更简洁。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-6ckfe0i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6ckfe0i","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-q9ma2c6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-q9ma2c6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"int result = (*add_ptr)(5, 3); // 显式解引用调用\nstd::cout \u003c\u003c “Result of add: ” \u003c\u003c result \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出: 8\n\ngreet_ptr(“Alice”); // 隐式解引用调用\n// 或者\n(*greet_ptr)(“Bob”); // 显式解引用调用\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-uky6jtq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uky6jtq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 函数指针的常见用途"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mglo3f1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mglo3f1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"函数指针在 C++ 中有多种应用场景，尤其是在需要"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"回调机制"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"或"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运行时选择行为"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l5piukm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l5piukm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.1 回调函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ckckwuu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ckckwuu","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将一个函数指针作为参数传递给另一个函数，让被调用的函数在特定时机执行这个传入的函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-vnk08bq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vnk08bq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例：排序算法中的比较函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ftks2on","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ftks2on","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 比较函数类型定义\ntypedef bool (*CompareFunc)(int, int);\n\n// 冒泡排序函数，接受一个比较函数指针\nvoid bubbleSort(int arr[], int n, CompareFunc compare) {\n    for (int i = 0; i \u003c n - 1; ++i) {\n        for (int j = 0; j \u003c n - i - 1; ++j) {\n            if (compare(arr[j], arr[j+1])) { // 使用传入的比较函数\n                std::swap(arr[j], arr[j+1]);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// 升序比较函数\nbool compareAsc(int a, int b) {\n    return a \u003e b; // 如果 a \u003e b，则交换 (升序)\n}\n\n// 降序比较函数\nbool compareDesc(int a, int b) {\n    return a \u003c b; // 如果 a \u003c b，则交换 (降序)\n}\n\nint main() {\n    int arr1[] = {5, 2, 8, 1, 9};\n    int arr2[] = {5, 2, 8, 1, 9};\n \tint n = sizeof(arr1) / sizeof(arr1[0]);\n\n    bubbleSort(arr1, n, compareAsc); // 升序排序\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c “Ascending: “;\n    for (int i = 0; i \u003c n; ++i) std::cout \u003c\u003c arr1[i] \u003c\u003c ” “; // 1 2 5 8 9\n\n    bubbleSort(arr2, n, compareDesc); // 降序排序\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c “\\nDescending: “;\n    for (int i = 0; i \u003c n; ++i) std::cout \u003c\u003c arr2[i] \u003c\u003c ” “; // 9 8 5 2 1\n\n    return 0;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qd24eyb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qd24eyb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.2 状态机"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3l15jyx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3l15jyx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将不同状态对应的处理函数存储在函数指针数组中，根据当前状态调用相应的函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9y9lfqb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9y9lfqb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ujcwste","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ujcwste","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"enum State { STATE_A, STATE_B, STATE_C };\n\nvoid handleStateA() { std::cout \u003c\u003c “Handling State A” \u003c\u003c std::endl; }\n\nvoid handleStateB() { std::cout \u003c\u003c “Handling State B” \u003c\u003c std::endl; }\n\nvoid handleStateC() { std::cout \u003c\u003c “Handling State C” \u003c\u003c std::endl; }\n\n// 函数指针数组\nvoid (*stateHandlers[])() = { handleStateA, handleStateB, handleStateC };\n\nint main() {\n    State current_state = STATE_A;\n    stateHandlers[current_state](); // 调用 handleStateA\n    current_state = STATE_B;\n    stateHandlers[current_state](); // 调用 handleStateB\n    return 0;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dh6kwee","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dh6kwee","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5 函数指针的局限性与现代 C++ 替代方案"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-qa8qmbh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-qa8qmbh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管函数指针非常强大，但它们也有一些局限性："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-a26fono","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-a26fono","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-fwxkt7p","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fwxkt7p","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-alf8l6y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-alf8l6y","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法复杂："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 声明和使用语法相对复杂，容易出错。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-36pgtlx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-36pgtlx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-azb27ff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-azb27ff","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"类型安全："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 必须严格匹配函数的签名，否则会导致编译错误。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-t1rom6l","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-t1rom6l","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-40qynwk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-40qynwk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无法捕获上下文："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 函数指针只能指向全局函数或静态成员函数，无法直接捕获其所在作用域的局部变量。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-42zzbl7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-42zzbl7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现代 C++ 提供了更灵活、更安全的替代方案："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-d90i6zd","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-d90i6zd","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-1tcdb1y","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1tcdb1y","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6frjsdl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6frjsdl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::function"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"(C++11)："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 一个通用的函数包装器，可以存储任何可调用对象（函数指针、函数对象、Lambda 表达式、成员函数指针）。它提供了更好的类型安全性和灵活性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-6w3f8ae","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6w3f8ae","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-3zi01pz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3zi01pz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Lambda 表达式 (C++11)："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 匿名函数，可以直接在代码中定义，并且可以捕获其所在作用域的变量，非常适合作为回调函数。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-k61379t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k61379t","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ho1waib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ho1waib","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"成员函数指针："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 专门用于指向类的非静态成员函数，语法更复杂，需要通过对象实例来调用。"}]}]}]}]}